{"tid":1117910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國咩都假】失戀女買兇殺負心男 「國際殺手」竟然係工人","createTime":"2019-04-21T04:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T09:27:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d50ec42a9eff8c4ac27b47af530dc9587b876285","tid":1117910,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"內地假貨無處不在！江蘇常熟市一名女子，為了報復男友偷食，且另娶他人，竟想到買兇殺人，但她萬萬沒料到，她僱用的「國際殺手」，竟然是假冒的。<br />\n這宗買兇殺人案發生於上個月，涉案的謝姓女子與男友拍拖1年，其間經常吵架。早前，兩人再度鬧翻，男友卻沒有如以往一樣哄她。謝女於是到男友家求和，竟意外得知男友早已變心，還經相睇認識了另1名女子，兩人拍拖兩個多月，年底就要結婚。<br />\n謝女震驚之餘，怒不可遏，決定報復負心漢。她透過網絡聯絡到廣東一名自稱「國際殺手」的杜姓男子，要求對方將其男友打至受傷1年，隨後又追加要將第三者打成終身殘廢。杜男先開價1.8萬人民幣（下同，約2.1萬港元），並要求對方先付3,000元（約3,509港元）定金，謝女依約向杜男匯出定金。<br />\n惟翌日，謝女又改變原來計劃，要求杜男把其男友與第三者全部殺死，杜男把價碼提高到3萬元（約3.5萬港元），還要求謝女匯2,000元（約2,339港元）定金。<br />\n警方在網上發現這宗「交易」後，於上月5日循線索到深圳一間工廠拘捕杜男。負責調查的常熟市公安局網絡警察大隊警員栾翰文坦言，當時根本未有掌握疑犯的身份，只知道僱主和兇手是通過網絡聯繫的。經進一步調查才發現，杜男根本不是甚麼國際職業殺手，他只是一名普通工人。杜男還指，自己一開始就沒有想過要殺人，只是想詐騙謝女。<br />\n據悉，杜男因涉嫌詐騙，目前正被刑事拘留。而謝女被警方拘捕後承認意圖買兇殺人，警方早前以涉嫌故意殺人罪，正式將她逮捕。<br />\n內地不少網友對於這宗離奇的買兇殺人案都感到不解，留言說：「電影看多了吧！」「一個敢僱，一個敢接。」也有網友拿百度、淘寶開玩笑，問這名國際殺手是否「百度認證V」「淘寶上僱用的嗎」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190420/large/1555773976_6641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190420%2Flarge%2F1555773976_6641.jpg&h=16364987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜姓男子被警方踢爆，根本是冒牌國際殺手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190421/59510576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F59510576&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTApq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=5897681b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F59510576&h=d65ad130\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190421/59510576</a>"},{"pid":"1f47ca4d38bfb17251e0c786826106dde347408b","tid":1117910,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3131dd1deb166187836e878a9ecf0a27dafdf03","tid":1117910,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350b441b27db38eba0fd429cec93251bd649bf51","tid":1117910,"uid":53122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"只有騙子是真的"},{"pid":"a3add21f3b87492de067cc27c47235b28070577d","tid":1117910,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"淘寶殺手"},{"pid":"52e98fb5230860fcd8b22a30b8c726b082ae9231","tid":1117910,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3add21f3b87492de067cc27c47235b28070577d","tid":1117910,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"淘寶殺手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0947912cec2b32312adeb29caee25e1b71f35988","tid":1117910,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/DlUD-qTiCt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDlUD-qTiCt4&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTApq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=cccbafbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/DlUD-qTiCt4</a><br />\n<br />\n金牌殺手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73f17c42a12a7fa10a4606bf6b0e38d85c018f9","tid":1117910,"uid":1800